snippet.title: Impious Pumpkins Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1774080/Impious_Pumpkins/

Impious Pumpkins is a cute/spooky real time strategy game where you take control of your own ghostly army to defend their resting places from hordes of evil pumpkins!
